<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- hyạ nmsẖwạ lblạd bʿydh nḥkw llnạs ḥkạytnạ ạljdydh ạlnạs ạlly ʿạysẖh fy ạlạ̉ḥzạn llnạs ạlmḥtạjh llgẖfrạn
 ạlqrạr- ʿndy kẖbr ʿndy dbạrh ạlmsyḥ gẖfr hdẖy ạlbsẖạrh
 2- nbdạ̉ bḥkạyẗ ạ̉dm wḥwạʾ wdʿwẗ ạ̹brạhym mn ạwl mrẗ
 nḥkylhm qṣẗ sẖʿb ạllh wḥfẓ ạlwṣạyạ wạlbrkạt
 3- nkẖtm bqṣẗ ạlmsyḥ wmḥbth lkl ạlạ̉ʿdạʾ
 yạ kẖwyạ rạjʿ rạhw ạ̉kyd mạ tqsy qlbk wtwly ʿnyd</lyrics>
<title>hyạ nmsẖw</title>
